	<br />
	<p class="pb-2 pt-6 text-4xl font-bold">
		Welcome to my outlandish anarchic-vegan-urbanist-phenomenological utopia
	</p>
	<div class="text-sm">
		<p class="py-2">
			Welcome. I'm a philosopher turned NASA software engineer. I'm pursuing a career at <span
				class="font-black text-orange-600"><a href="https://www.jpl.nasa.gov/">NASA's Jet Propulsion Laboratory</a></span
			> working on projects supporting robotic space exploration of our solar system. I
			write about topics ranging from anarchic urbanism, transportation, the politics of space exploration,
			the philosophy of animal liberation, software engineering, and phenomenology. I hope you find something of interest on my site.
		</p>
